    "1 Overall structure of proposed model Fig. 2 The structure of BiLSTM-CRF model and the CRF layer.",
    "Within the Embedding layer, unstructured text undergoes tokenization, and each token is transformed into numerical form using an embedding technique.",
    "This work employs two distinct embedding techniques: FastText and BERT-based embeddings.",
    "The vector representations of unstructured text are subsequently input into the acrshortbilstm model.",
    "The output of the acrshortbilstm layer is then utilized as input for the CRF layer, which serves the purpose of classifying named entities."
